## Optional OpenAI setup

Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and add your key:

```env
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here
```

The application works without an OpenAI key. The key is used only for an optional AI explanation of the MCP trace.

## Training note

This application is an educational simulator. It models the important MCP concepts—agent, client, server, tools, transport, authentication, and structured results—without requiring participants to configure a production MCP server.

